body:
This change standardizes JSON output to example given, as well as
codemaid and online lint tools.

Sample object used for testing:

```powershell
@{
foo = @{
first = 'a'
second = 'bbbbbbbb'
}
barbarbarbar = @{
first = 'a'
second = 'bbbbbbbb'
NestedArray = @(
'Test3'
'Test4'
'Test5'
3
4
)
NestedObject = @{
MoreObject = 'AnotherObject'
TestBool = $true
}
}
array = @(
'Thing1'
'Thing2'
)
dan = 15
} | ConvertTo-Json
```
